<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/656535-how-do-i-move-bk-from-curt-read-to-read">How do I move bk. From curt.read to read?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_656535'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F25343675-the-forgotten-recipe">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/656535-how-do-i-move-bk-from-curt-read-to-read">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/656535-how-do-i-move-bk-from-curt-read-to-read">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/11185132-amanda"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1431001083i/11185132._UX100_CR0,8,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/11185132-amanda">Amanda</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Hi Barbara. To move a book from the &quot;Cuurently Reading&quot; to &quot;Read&quot; shelf, you can either update your progress on the book and click the &quot;I&apos;ve finished <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Hi Barbara. To move a book from the "Cuurently Reading" to "Read" shelf, you can either update your progress on the book and click the "I've finished this book" button, or you can click the drop down arrow next to where it says "Currently Reading" and choose "Read", which will move it. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

