<span id="freeTextContainer183878248660450729">I have been enjoying Amy Clipston&apos;s stories for many years and THE FORGOTTEN RECIPE is exactly why. The twists and turns in Veronica and Jason&apos;s lives pop up when you least expect them. Amy pulls you right in and makes you feel as if you are right there experiencing all the heart wrenching feelings that her characters are. When I hear that Amy Clipston has a new book coming out, I run to it. She is quickly becoming one of my favorite Amish authors and I devour her stories very quickly. I love ho</span>
  <span id="freeText183878248660450729" style="display:none">I have been enjoying Amy Clipston's stories for many years and THE FORGOTTEN RECIPE is exactly why. The twists and turns in Veronica and Jason's lives pop up when you least expect them. Amy pulls you right in and makes you feel as if you are right there experiencing all the heart wrenching feelings that her characters are. When I hear that Amy Clipston has a new book coming out, I run to it. She is quickly becoming one of my favorite Amish authors and I devour her stories very quickly. I love how her stories allow me to escape my reality and puts me right in the middle of Amish country. <br /><br />ARC provided by Netgalley for an honest review.</span>
