<span id="freeTextContainer10618362701498758675">Hi, I’m Amy Clipston. I am an author of Amish and Christian fiction with HarperCollins Christian Publishing. Most of my books focus on the Amish community, faith, and love. I also write romance novels and young adult inspirational stories. <br/><br/>My books include:<br/><br/>Kauffman Amish Bakery Series<br/>•	A Gift of Grace (2009)<br/>•	A Promise of Hope (2010)<br/>•	A Place of Peace (2011)<br/>•	A Life of Joy (2012)<br/>•	A Season of Love</span>
